<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V2.0//EN" "http://forrest.apache.org/dtd/document-v20.dtd">
<document> 
  <header> 
    <title>Welcome to the org.apache.forrest.plugin.XHTML-output Plugin</title> 
  </header> 
  <body> 
    <section>
      <title>Apache Forrest - org.apache.forrest.plugin.XHTML-output Plugin</title>
      <p>This plugin generates XHTML pages from your Forrest documents. This 
      plugin is included in a new forrest project by default.</p>
      
      <p>In order to use this plugin you need do nothing special, simply 
      request a document with a <code>.html</code> extension and Forrest
      will do the rest.</p>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>